Rights groups report widespread sexual violence against Palestinians in Israeli prisons
description: One-third of the 21 detainees who spoke to the Israeli NGO B'Tselem after their release said they had been subjected to violence, including forced undressing, blows to the genitals, and anal penetration. Other NGOs and UN agencies have reported similar accounts. Israel has denied any systematic mistreatment.

headline: 'Article 49.3': How France's government can pass a budget without a vote

headline: In one year, Trump has imposed a culture of impunity
description: Since returning to the White House, the American president has exempted himself from all rules, both domestically and internationally. This sense of impunity now permeates his entire administration.
